'''Branden Fitelson''' (born August 17, 1969 in [[Syracuse, NY]]) is an American philosopher and Distinguished Professor of [[Philosophy]] at [[Northeastern University]]. He is known for his expertise on [[formal epistemology]] and [[philosophy of science]].<ref>{{cite web|title=Philosophy Phriday [On a Tuesday]: Video Interview With Branden Fitelson|url=https://dailyant.com/2017/12/19/philosophy-phriday-on-a-tuesday-video-interview-with-branden-fitelson/|website=[[The Daily Ant]]|accessdate=25 March 2018|date=20 December 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Brief Biography of Branden Fitelson|url=https://infidels.org/library/modern/branden_fitelson/fitelson-bio.html|website=infidels.org|accessdate=25 March 2018|language=en}}</ref>
